name: iShares Silver Bullion ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of the Fund is to replicate the performance of the price of physical silver bullion, less the Funds fees and expenses. To achieve its investment objective the investment strategy of the Fund is to invest in long term holdings of unencumbered silver bullion in 1,000 troy ounce international bar sizes and to not speculate with regard to short term changes in silver bullion prices.
